  "summary": "**網格圖題目核心技巧**：\n- 方向陣列：`int dirs[4][2] = {{0,1}, {0,-1}, {1,0}, {-1,0}};`\n- 邊界檢查：`x >= 0 && x < m && y >= 0 && y < n`\n- 訪問陣列：`vector<vector<bool>> visited(m, vector<bool>(n, false));`\n\n**本題單涵蓋**：\n- DFS\n- BFS\n- 綜合應用\n\n```cpp\n// 網格圖 DFS/BFS 模板\nint dirs[4][2] = {{0, 1}, {0, -1}, {1, 0}, {-1, 0}};\n\n// DFS 遍歷連通塊\nvoid dfs(vector<vector<int>>& grid, int x, int y) {\n    int m = grid.size(), n = grid[0].size();\n    grid[x][y] = 0; // 標記已訪問\n    for (auto& d : dirs) {\n        int nx = x + d[0], ny = y + d[1];\n        if (nx >= 0 && nx < m && ny >= 0 && ny < n && grid[nx][ny]) {\n            dfs(grid, nx, ny);\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n// BFS 求最短路\nint bfs(vector<vector<int>>& grid, int sx, int sy, int tx, int ty) {\n    int m = grid.size(), n = grid[0].size();\n    queue<pair<int, int>> q;\n    q.push({sx, sy});\n    grid[sx][sy] = 0;\n    int step = 0;\n    while (!q.empty()) {\n        int sz = q.size();\n        while (sz--) {\n            auto [x, y] = q.front();\n            q.pop();\n            if (x == tx && y == ty) {\n                return step;\n            }\n            for (auto& d : dirs) {\n                int nx = x + d[0], ny = y + d[1];\n                if (nx >= 0 && nx < m && ny >= 0 && ny < n && grid[nx][ny]) {\n                    grid[nx][ny] = 0;\n                    q.push({nx, ny});\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        step++;\n    }\n    return -1;\n}\n```"
